{"tid":1789340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"死線係24/12，之後我想像唔到會發生咩事","createTime":"2019-12-19T10:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T00:47:52.000Z","uid":78020,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e086ef0fce0c40417556cac891d2de02f4418d2b","tid":1789340,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"抖夠啦<br />\n抖夠啦<br />\n想試制度內方法唔代表要街頭降溫<br />\n想靜靜雞唔代表外判責任比勇武小隊<br />\n想休息唔代表要回歸日常<br />\n抗爭日常化唔代表反抗方法降格成日常生活選擇<br />\n唔想再有人送頭唔代表要放棄半年手足作出嘅犧牲，佢地唔係為左要我地同情心爆發先犧牲自己<br />\n<br />\n我唔知大家出返黎街頭會用咩方法反抗<br />\n我淨係知勇武同和理非唔係身份，係技能<br />\n而就算係無勇武技能嘅人，都會一齊走上街頭，和勇不分<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n反抗<br />\n報仇"},{"pid":"f4c05abae2977d5bf674788648a205bd03027468","tid":1789340,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c408def2e84d54288fe37b4b8d2e847ab816538b","tid":1789340,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ac52398fd06610d8dfb4cc4f3341ac7563ee6a1","tid":1789340,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲"},{"pid":"b006fd317d96d90900d85c4ab45aeb699f4924d1","tid":1789340,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:12:16.000Z","msg":"嬲就要行動"},{"pid":"da39e1bade0809a8a942db4fca2c57a5ac69b477","tid":1789340,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對准18區商場"},{"pid":"e32b962906709d0bcf4e69382cd776478c8756d1","tid":1789340,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj